      <hedline>
        <hl1>Boom Box</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Richard J Werther letter on Michael Lewis's August 13 article disputes assertion that no one knows how to program a VCR (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I suppose the pace of change described in Lewis's article will be frightening to some. What scared me more was the assertion that no one knows how to program a VCR! My technical skill is at best limited, but I've never had a problem with any VCR I've owned.</p>
        <p>Richard J. Werther  Novi, Mich.</p>
      </block>
